Package fr.univartois.cril.approximation.util.collections.heaps

package fr.univartois.cril.approximation.util.collections.heaps
The fr.univartois.cril.orpheus.utils.collections.heaps package contains the classes defining heap data-structures having an efficient access to their elements.
